      "conclusion": "CONFIRMED: 59% gap was a measurement bug. Cross-stream tile counter zero_() not visible to WS kernel on MI300X non-coherent L2. Fix: run reset on same stream as matmul. True warm-vs-rotating gap is ~6%. True RCCL overlap slowdown is 12-17% (from CU contention + memory BW sharing, not cache thrashing)."
